---
title: Ghoulish Goulash Style Pork Pasta with Monster Garlic Bread
description: Family feasts don't get much creepier than this Ghoulish Goulash Style Pork Pasta. Packed with delicious ingredients and served with a scary good side of Monster Garlic Bread, spooky season just got frightfully tasty.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W43_UK_R27163-3_Main_low_2-c099b828.jpg
